rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0001
rows.name:
Well, they certainly got us good
this time...

rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0002
rows.name:
We had a bit of an incident here.
The containers were attacked by
Volff in the middle of the night.

rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0003
rows.name:
They didn't manage to get at the
contents, but they ruined the locks on
some, and others won't even close now.

rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0004
rows.name:
And we're not talking just a couple,
either. The number of damaged
containers is in the double digits.

rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0005
rows.name:
If we don't fix them up quickly, it'll
start affecting the transport schedules,
but with so many containers to repair...

rows.label: tlk45600551_10_msg0006
rows.name:
All right. I'll let you handle it!
You'd better do a good job, though!
